    "en": {
      "title": "Two deaths in fuel row",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two more people were killed while standing in the fuel line. A 64-year-old man has died in Madhugama, Belawat.",
        "In this case, one of the people who was waiting in line to get fuel at a fuel station in Kinnyal died yesterday (22) around 12 noon.",
        "49-year-old Muhammad Ramlan Sharif from Kinnia Nudchenai area is the deceased.",
        "It is noteworthy that he was waiting in the fuel line for more than 24 hours"
      ],
